Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:34.93,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}A universe alive with sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:40.56,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}a billion voices, a billion stars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:45.65,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}An ancient song long forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:50.74,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}ringing out across eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:56.37,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Longing to find a sense of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:17:01.83,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}we ran like crazy from the start
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:05.25,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Perhaps we were both too blind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:11.59,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}to ever see the pain we caused
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:18.56,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Some may say we're being weak
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:24.23,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}to fantasize and dream of what the future could be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.07,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}We've always held on hope
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:33.12,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}to change this crumbled world and its stubborn way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:40.21,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}We've laid the building blocks for tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:48.09,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}We crossed paths in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:52.88,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}And it doesn't have to mean a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.47,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}But let me know you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.97,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}let me reach out to you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:03.44,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}You're my everything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:10.82,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Another star burns to its core and falling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:15.03,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}its orbit draws a story born
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:23.87,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Its story shines upon someone far away from here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:30.21,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Have no fear, oh let us meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:35.68,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}somewhere far beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:08.25,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Finding our time has gone, we've kept on going
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:12.59,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Since we had never further than we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:18.64,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Everyone we've passed by is a part of our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:25.69,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Right now I can hear their voices too
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:28.19,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Is it true
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:35.28,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}We crossed paths in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:39.87,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}And it doesn't have to mean a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.79,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}But let me know you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:46.62,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}let me reach out to you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:50.54,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}You're my everything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:54.46,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}We're mere human souls
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:58.18,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}And some day we'll vanish,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:02.47,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}And fade into the ever after
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.18,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}So let us live for now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:11.23,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}let us sing aloud and clear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:17.40,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Have no fear, oh we will meet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:23.99,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}somewhere far beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:28.24,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}もしもあの改札の前で　立ち止まらず歩いていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:33.67,IN - JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9}君の顔も知らずのまま　幸せに生きていただろうか
